Package com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude.batch

Class BatchReader

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude.batch.BatchReader
public class BatchReader extends Object
BatchReader provides methods to parse BatchRequests and EventResponses contained in Nodes of a SOAPMessage generated and saved to a file by a BatchWriter.

The file that will be read by this reader should have a SOAPMessage that can be extracted from a xml format file.

1.0
